Package: de.unigoettingen.sub.be.ous.print.layout

[Groovy] Class Xml2Parser

      • de.unigoettingen.sub.be.ous.print.layout.Xml2Parser

      • Converts XML representation of a layout into a parser and returns a Groovy class representing the generated parser
